The paper is about detecting shilling attacks in recommendation systems, which is a common problem in information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML) applications. Therefore, cs.IR and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with security issues, which falls under the category of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR).
